  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the<span class=\"italic\"><span class=\"italic \"> xy</span></span>-plane, the graph of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals 3 x squared minus 14 x\"></span></span> intersects the graph of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals x\"></span></span> at the points <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"with coordinates zero comma zero\"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, comma a\"></span><span class=\"math_expression \"></span>. What is the value of <span class=\"italic\">a</span> ?</p>\n",
